    "summary": "\ud835\udde0\ud835\uddee\ud835\uddfb\ud835\ude02\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddf9\ud835\uddee \ud835\uddd5\ud835\uddd8\ud835\udde5\ud835\udde0\ud835\udde8\ud835\uddd7\ud835\uddd8\ud835\udded/ \ud835\udde5&\ud835\uddd7 \ud835\udde3\ud835\uddff\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddf1\ud835\ude02\ud835\uddf0\ud835\ude01 & \ud835\udde3\ud835\uddff\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddf0\ud835\uddf2\ud835\ude00\ud835\ude00 \ud835\uddd8\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddf4\ud835\uddf6\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddff\n- I am a Chemical Engineer (UNLP, Argentina) and I completed a Master's in Food Engineering (ESA Angers and ISARA Lyon, France)\n- I have 8+ years of experience managing the development and optimization of products and processes in a multinational food industry (Lactalis Group, 1st global dairy company).\n- I developed my R&D career in different countries: France, Uruguay, Brazil and Argentina\n- I am fluent in multiple languages \u200b\u200b(Spanish, French, English and Portuguese)\n- I am passionate about being able to contribute to developing innovative and healthy products and at the same time sharing experience with colleagues from different countries/cultures\n\n\u2728Of my last positions as \ud835\udde5&\ud835\uddd7 \ud835\udde3\ud835\uddff\ud835\uddfc\ud835\uddf7\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddf0\ud835\ude01 \ud835\udde0\ud835\uddee\ud835\uddfb\ud835\uddee\ud835\uddf4\ud835\uddf2\ud835\uddff I highlight:\n- Leadership of 10-15 R&D projects in parallel, contemplating 7 factories in total in 4 different countries (Argentina, Brazil, Chile, Uruguay)\n- Management of the different stages of the product development process: from validation of briefs, through pilot and industrial trials to product launch\n- Carrying out 6 to 20 industrial trials/month, with their technical reports, sensory evaluations and corresponding action plans\n- Coordination of project meetings with the factory team (weekly or fortnightly) and monthly meeting with different cross sectors (marketing, industrial, quality,...)\n- Technical assistance to the factory to solve recipe, process and/or product quality issues",
